@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qpmlqp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 + ((v0 + 0.04 - v1 + 0.69) - v2))
    v2 = (0.82 + wp.cos((tmp + 0.63 / tmp + 0.43)))
    v2 = 0.71
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.42 - v2 + 0.65) / tmp) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.63 + v0 + 0.91)))
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
